    "actor": "https://uofa.net/morrison/actor/credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 guidance for a Class II device at MRL 2 with Medium model influence. Validation evidence demonstrates RH predictions within 7% of in-vitro measurements across all 5 COU operating points, satisfying the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. An uncertainty quantification campaign (summarised in validation result narratives) provided supplementary confidence that input parameter variability does not invalidate the credibility conclusion. The assessment team concludes that the CFD model is sufficiently credible to support the regulatory submission decision.",
